title: Andy Ngo | Bret Weinsteins DarkHorse Podcast #1
description:
For the inaugural episode of Bret Weinstein's DarkHorse Podcast, Bret sits down with Andy Ngo to discuss the recent attack he suffered from Antifa during protests in downtown Portland. This is Mr. Ngo's first long-form interview after he was hospitalized for a brain hemorrhage sustained at the hands of Antifa rioters in downtown Portland, on June 29, 2019.

Follow Andy on Twitter: https://twitter.com/MrAndyNgo
